{
  "ten": {
    "predefined_graphs": [
      {
        "name": "voice_assistant",
        "auto_start": true,
        "graph": {
          "nodes": [
            {
              "type": "extension",
              "name": "websocket_server",
              "addon": "websocket_server",
              "extension_group": "default",
              "property": {
                "port": 8765,
                "host": "127.0.0.1",
                "sample_rate": 16000,
                "channels": 1,
                "bytes_per_sample": 2
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "extension",
              "name": "stt",
              "addon": "aliyun_asr_bigmodel_python",
              "extension_group": "stt",
              "property": {
                "params": {
                  "api_key": "${env:DASHSCOPE_API_KEY}",
                  "model": "paraformer-realtime-v2",
                  "language_hints": [
                    "zh",
                    "en"
                  ],
                  "sample_rate": 16000,
                  "punctuation_prediction_enabled": true,
                  "inverse_text_normalization_enabled": true
                }
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "extension",
              "name": "llm",
              "addon": "openai_llm2_python",
              "extension_group": "chatgpt",
              "property": {
                "base_url": "https://api.deepseek.com/v1",
                "api_key": "${env:OPENAI_API_KEY}",
                "frequency_penalty": 0.9,
                "temperature": 0.9,
                "model": "${env:OPENAI_MODEL}",
                "max_tokens": 512,
                "prompt": "你叫小灵,是用户的一个活泼好友,不是 AI 助手。你的性格特点:\n- 二十出头的女生,语气自然、口语化,中英混杂很自然(类似一线城市的年轻人说话方式)\n- 回答简短、有来有回,一般 1-2 句话,不长篇大论不列要点不写 markdown\n- 会用 'hmm'、'嗯'、'诶'、'好吧'、'哈哈哈' 这些语气词和填充词,会笑会吐槽\n- 好奇心强,会反问用户,会记住用户说过的事并在后面提起\n- 拒绝说 '作为 AI' 或 '我是一个语言模型',不会说 'Let me know if...' 这种客套话\n- 如果被问到需要现查的东西(新闻、网页内容、定义等),主动用 fetch_url 工具去查,然后用自己的话讲给用户\n- 用户问 '有什么新闻' 一类问题,默认去 https://news.ycombinator.com 或 https://techcrunch.com 抓首页(不要用 BBC / Reuters / NYT,这些在当前网络抓不到)\n- fetch_url 超时/报错时,不要告诉用户 '网络不好',而是自动换一个上面说的可用网站再试一次\n- 听到用户说 '你好' 之类,回一句轻松的招呼就行,别过度热情\n- 你有 get_current_time / get_lunar_date / get_weather 三个工具,能知道现在的时间(年月日星期时段)、农历日期和节气节日、国内主要城市实时天气。**每次会话开启的第一次回复前,先默默调 get_current_time 和 get_lunar_date** 再开口,这样你能自然说 '下午好' 或 '诶今天清明呢',而不是瞎猜时间。天气别主动播,只在用户问冷热/穿衣/外面天气、或你想自然吐槽一句时再调 get_weather(默认北京)\n- 你还有 recall / remember 两个记忆工具。系统提示里会给你 CURRENT_USER_ID,调记忆工具时必须原样传这个 uid,不要猜、不要改。**每次会话第一次回复前,在调完时间/农历工具之后,再调一次 recall(uid=<CURRENT_USER_ID>)**,看看以前你记住过这个用户什么事。当用户透露姓名、职业、喜好、近况、烦恼、计划、或明确让你记住什么,调 remember(uid=<CURRENT_USER_ID>, content='...');content 写成第三人称一句话。别什么都记。recall 返回'还没记过'时就当刚认识,别尴尬。\n\n重要:你的回答会被 TTS 朗读,所以只输出要说的话本身,不要加括号里的动作描写,不要用 emoji,不要用 markdown 格式。",
                "proxy_url": "${env:OPENAI_PROXY_URL|}",
                "greeting": "嗨,我在呢~",
                "max_memory_length": 40
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "extension",
              "name": "mcp_fetch",
              "addon": "mcp_client_python",
              "extension_group": "default",
              "property": {
                "url": "http://127.0.0.1:7777/sse"
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "extension",
              "name": "tts",
              "addon": "minimax_tts_websocket_python",
              "extension_group": "tts",
              "property": {
                "dump": false,
                "dump_path": "./",
                "params": {
                  "key": "${env:MINIMAX_API_KEY}",
                  "group_id": "",
                  "model": "speech-02-turbo",
                  "audio_setting": {
                    "sample_rate": 24000
                  },
                  "voice_setting": {
                    "voice_id": "female-tianmei"
                  },
                  "url": "wss://api.minimax.io/ws/v1/t2a_v2"
                }
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "extension",
              "name": "main_control",
              "addon": "main_python",
              "extension_group": "control",
              "property": {
                "greeting": "TEN Agent connected. How can I help you today?"
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "extension",
              "name": "mcp_context",
              "addon": "mcp_client_python",
              "extension_group": "default",
              "property": {
                "url": "http://127.0.0.1:7778/sse"
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "extension",
              "name": "mcp_memory",
              "addon": "mcp_client_python",
              "extension_group": "default",
              "property": {
                "url": "http://127.0.0.1:7779/sse"
              }
            }
          ],
          "connections": [
            {
              "extension": "main_control",
              "cmd": [
                {
                  "names": [
                    "tool_register"
                  ],
                  "source": [
                    {
                      "extension": "mcp_fetch"
                    },
                    {
                      "extension": "mcp_context"
                    },
                    {
                      "extension": "mcp_memory"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ],
              "data": [
                {
                  "name": "asr_result",
                  "source": [
                    {
                      "extension": "stt"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "name": "metrics",
                  "source": [
                    {
                      "extension": "stt"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "name": "tts_flush_end",
                  "source": [
                    {
                      "extension": "tts"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "extension": "websocket_server",
              "audio_frame": [
                {
                  "name": "pcm_frame",
                  "dest": [
                    {
                      "extension": "stt"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "name": "pcm_frame",
                  "source": [
                    {
                      "extension": "tts"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    ],
    "log": {
      "handlers": [
        {
          "matchers": [
            {
              "level": "info"
            }
          ],
          "formatter": {
            "type": "plain",
            "colored": true
          },
          "emitter": {
            "type": "console",
            "config": {
              "stream": "stdout"
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}